reviewText: Great movie and i was surprised at the quality of the video......5 stars.....Thanks
Cubs Win, Cubs Win, Cubs Win, 2016 World Champions.  A Classic Joe E. Brown
Our son and family loved it!

One of the best old time baseball movies.  Real Americana  My grandfather played semi-pro ball with Joey Brown.  Joey was a very good ball player and we have a federation ball field named after him in North Toledo.  You will enjoy the start of the movie with Sterling Hayden answering the phone, when the big leagues call for Joey
